title: NFL Preseason, NFL Top 100 Top Spot, Cowboys playoffs? Weekend Watchlist, and Brady is back!
itunes:title: NFL Preseason, NFL Top 100 Top Spot, Cowboys playoffs? Weekend Watchlist, and Brady is back!
description:
The Good Morning Football Podcast begins with NFL preseason action between the Packers/Chiefs and 49ers/Texans.  Hosts Jamie Erdahl, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and Super Bowl Champion Jason McCourty discuss who should be named the #1 player in the NFL and who will be named #1.  Jerry Jones discusses the Tyron Smith injury and still predicts the Cowboys in the playoffs.  Peter gives his top 5 players to watch for in this weekend's preseason action.  The table debates possible reasons the Bucs could miss the playoffs and look forward to Tom Brady's return to the team.

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
